  * src/makelogline.c: Fix for WYSIWYG_ONCE  
  - points were not written for WYSIWYG_ONCE

  * src/getsummary.c, src/writecabrillo.c: simplify  
  - use get_nr_of_points() and get_nr_of_mults() to calculate claimed score 

